snippet.title: Attitude | Stand-up Comedy by Ravi Gupta
snippet.description:
Guess who’s Back?
The attitude king Ravi Gupta is back with his New Video. In this video, I talk about how my life has completely changed ever since my video went viral and How Humility has been replaced by arrogance. Yes, that’s true, I am not the same guy anymore. I know I am being Naive and You as usual are smart enough to sense the sarcasm in this video. 

I hope enjoy the video & do whatever you can in your capacity to promote it. 

Ticket link for the live show - https://in.bookmyshow.com/mumbai/events/kal-ki-chinta-nahi-karta-ft-ravi-gupta/ET00329412/bookingStep/venue

Follow me on Instagram - https://instagram.com/shudhdesicomic?...

New YouTube Channel for Shorts - https://appopener.com/yt/2o8lwmpry

Song CREDITS:
Concept, Composition, Lyrics and Rap: Rajat Sood 'Yaara'
Vocals: Pawan Singh, Ravi Gupta
Music: fortem, fetar
Mixed and Mastered by: Bharath

Credits - Shot and recorded by The Habitat

snippet.title: Parents | Stand-up Comedy by Ravi Gupta
snippet.description:
I am touring in india with my Stand up comedy solo "Kal Ki Chinta Nahi karta" Click on the link below to book tickets -
https://in.bookmyshow.com/events/kal-ki-chinta-nahi-karta-ft-ravi-gupta/ET00329412

About the Video -
The journey of this set started back in April 2020 when I moved back to my native place in UP. In this video, I talk about my parents and How I actually got to know them on a whole new level in the past 2 years. They mean the world to me so this video has some bizarre and funny tales about my world. I hope you like the video and if you are reading this description then I thank you for being there from day one.

snippet.title: Office | Stand-up Comedy  by Ravi Gupta
snippet.description:
The idea is to not sound too official while writing this description and This is what I expect should change in offices across the world. The tone and style of working is too robotic and that's what I make fun about in this office. Your Office , My office and pretty much all the offices But laughing a little bit is all okay but never hate the place that pays your bills , and never hate raccoons.

snippet.title: Job aur Passion | Stand Up Comedy By Ravi Gupta
snippet.description:
In this video, I talk about a phase of my life where things were not going that well and because of it I had to quit my job.
Due to this, my parents stopped respecting me and finally, we came on the same page when it comes to respecting each other.
Anyway if you found my misery funny then hit the like button and comment to boost my confidence.
Also, subscribe to my channel and press that bell icon.

Follow me on Instagram 
* https://www.instagram.com/shudhdesicomic/ *

Credits :
Venue: The Habitat 
Shot by: The Habitat team

snippet.description:
In this video, I talk about how tour guides have changed over the years But the autowalas remain the same. Also - 
Zindagi me zyada armaan nahi rahe hain mere. inhi kam armaano ke chakkar me video late daali. wo apni galti hai. Ab reguler videos aate rahenge. 
Abhi ke liye ek hi request hai aur ek hi armaan. Ye video dekh liya ho to niche link pe jaake pas follow kar lena instagram pe.
Bina mare meri aatma ko shanti m il jaayegi.

and if you like this video share with your friends, family( isme to gaali bhi nahi hai)
subscribe to the channel.
bell icon daba do.
milte hain agle video me.

localized.description:
I am touring in india with my Stand up comedy solo "Kal Ki Chinta Nahi karta" Click on the link below to book tickets -
https://in.bookmyshow.com/events/kal-ki-chinta-nahi-karta-ft-ravi-gupta/ET00329412

About the Video -
The journey of this set started back in April 2020 when I moved back to my native place in UP. In this video, I talk about my parents and How I actually got to know them on a whole new level in the past 2 years. They mean the world to me so this video has some bizarre and funny tales about my world. I hope you like the video and if you are reading this description then I thank you for being there from day one.

Follow me on Instagram for show updates and funny short videos -
